---
title: Paddy's Cheesy Pork Burger with Garlic & Herb Kumara Fries
description: We’ve taken the best parts of the American Southern BBQ experience – creamy sauce, aromatic herbs and spices – and added a juicy pork patty and soft buns to make a burger that y’all will love!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-american-pork-burgers-6b00bb3c.jpg
